# Force LF line endings for text files regardless of the checking-out
# machine's own git config (Git for Windows commonly defaults to
# core.autocrlf=true, which silently converts LF to CRLF on checkout) --
# found because crates/yadorilink-reporting/src/builder.rs's fixture tests
# compare an include_str!'d file's actual on-disk bytes against
# in-memory-generated JSON (always LF), and failed on their first-ever
# real Windows CI run for exactly this reason.
* text=auto eol=lf
